		<td><b>Re: SNES emu with &quot;Force NTSC/PAL&quot;?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />ZSNES and SNES9X have versions that support forcing NTSC or PAL mode as well. They are present at the loading screen.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
